'''[[metamorphic]] [[rock]]'''
#{{geology}} one of the major groups of rock that makes up the [[crust]] of the [[Earth]]; consists of [[preexisting]] rock mass in which new [[mineral]]s or [[texture]]s are formed at higher [[temperature]]s and greater [[pressure]]s than those present on the Earth's [[surface]]
